1. Try to write function in terms of the function like

 -> fibonacy : fib(n)=fib(n-1)+fib(n-2); then
               return fib(n-1)+fib(n-2);

 -> factorial : fact(n)=fact(n-1)*n;
                return fact(n-1)*n;

2. Then write base condition to break;
 
 -> for fibo : if(n==1) return 1, if(n==0) return 0;
 -> for fact : if(n==1) return 1;


            How recursion work

for every recurion call function store in stack like
 
==> in fibo(5)
     fib(4),fib(3),fib(2),......
     similarly in order of function call it store in stack 
     and return all in order from top and execute the remaining code below the function

    